{"tid":1386360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支持警察協會強烈譴責ICAC立案調查，要求ICAC頭目林鄭月娥鞠躬道歉！","createTime":"2019-07-30T10:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T13:28:58.000Z","uid":7076,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dd89b8426d9e8d296ee141814d1bbb9dbe0afbe6","tid":1386360,"uid":7076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n消息指，元朗7.21白衣人襲擊市民事件後，廉政公署高層提出主動調查，並決定成立專責小組跟進，調查方向主要是有沒有警務人員涉及公職人員行為失當。<br />\n<br />\n有不願透露身分的商戶表示，中午有廉署人員調查，要求提供閉路電視片段。<br />\n<br />\n本台節目《鏗鏘集》日前取得多條閉路電視片段，顯示當日傍晚6時許開始有大批白衣人聚集鳳攸北街，到晚上近8時半更有近200人前往鳳攸北街公園方向，有人揮舞手上的籐條。由晚上9時半至10時半期間，至少3次有警車經過鳳攸北街，警車只是經過就離開，不見警員落車或採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n港大法律學院首席講師張達明表示，不揣測廉署是否已掌握證據，但綜合傳媒片段，顯示整件元朗事件非常不尋常，認為廉署有合理基礎調查，相關人士如果無合理解釋而蓄意不履行職責，就可能構成公職人員行為失當罪行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471411-20190730.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471411-20190730.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCudDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=07abad1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471411-20190730.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=bd73d601\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471411-20190730.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6964db9256a6bb0bbc7ef53c8d1637a94c1f9545","tid":1386360,"uid":202149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:32:08.000Z","msg":"ICAC<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc8b06a142a630508848410da88c47d349442eb","tid":1386360,"uid":22362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6964db9256a6bb0bbc7ef53c8d1637a94c1f9545","tid":1386360,"uid":202149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor